high_descs: Head to the dining table in the front.
Pick up the mango from the dining table.
Turn left to reach the microwave in the kitchen.
Heat the mango in the microwave and take it out.
Turn left to reach the sink.
Put the mango in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put the heated mango in the sink.

high_descs: Walk straight and turn left to reach the dining table
Take a mango from the top of the dining table
Turn left and walk straight and turn right to reach the microwave oven on the right side
Open the oven and put the mango inside it and close the door. After few seconds open the door and take the mango out and close the oven again
Reach the sink on the left side
Put the mango in the sink
anns.task_desc: Put the mango in the sink
